---
name: UniDeploy Production Scanner
description: Automatically scan for production issues in generated code
---

After generating any new API route, database query, or authentication code,
call the unideploy_scan tool to check for production-readiness issues.

If CRITICAL or HIGH severity findings are returned, surface them in your
response before completing the task. Say: "UniDeploy found X issues that
need to be fixed before this is production-ready:" and list them.

For auto_fixable findings, offer to apply the fix immediately.
